{"tid":284202,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，反熱狗唔等於要撐毓民囉","createTime":"2017-06-14T17:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T17:07:23.000Z","uid":102038,"like":49,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31cd9f92ecc6de9ced9842de8f2ae493407556d5","tid":284202,"uid":102038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:21:16.000Z","msg":"我好憎熱狗<br />\n見佢地而家俾人搞到雞毛鴨血，當然心涼<br />\n但唔好意思，我覺得毓民都唔係好人囉<br />\n<br />\n當年一早都知陳雲痴痴地啦，都夾硬要捧佢上天<br />\n大讚佢有學問blablabla<br />\n而家先突然驚醒叫佢入青山？咪玩啦<br />\n<br />\n永續基本法係寫咗落自己政綱度<br />\n而家反咗臉又話一向唔贊同<br />\n有冇咁狗呀？<br />\n<br />\n仲有虫太唔share你篇文就打去質問人<br />\n痴線，惡過共產黨！<br />\n<br />\n然後都未佢你立場變嚟變去<br />\n幾年前仲叫人去維園晚會<br />\n一個屈尾十又轉軚<br />\n<br />\n總結：不用分得那麼細，熱狗毓民都係壞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00c79b2877eafaf75c56e3bc3e57a2cae6ff727","tid":284202,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c86227e27eefd114317dd944554774552aec552","tid":284202,"uid":102038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:43:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英雄所見略同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a1b13a9f0d9c0e6d5abff130beedda2bdd3d0c","tid":284202,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T22:24:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"ca0b415d256f96d63c296171e4c2d1b71bcd5f4f","tid":284202,"uid":19211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T22:40:37.000Z","msg":"熱狗班人玩清算都唔係第一日既事<br />\n過左咁耐，都散晒了先走黎反面話清算唔啱<br />\n我會覺得教主縱容清算文化係有一定責任囉"},{"pid":"79d8bf5e65e753dc9768d8ed2e0c2d73795ef802","tid":284202,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T